data.name: DescriptionLabel.Text
data.value: It is possible to graphically customize EsayLook by setting properties from this panel. Report snapshot management can also be driven by changing some default values.

data.name: WrmHistoryAutoDelEnabledCheckBox.Text
data.value: Allow automatic deletion for all report snapshots

data.name: WrmHistoryAutoDelCommentLabel.Text
data.value: Scheduler agent is needed in order to enable automatic deletion of reports history.

data.name: SnapshotHelpLabel.Text
data.value: Snapshots of a report are savings of its preceeding executions: they permit viewing data exactly "as they were" without launching the report again.
